tafsir[26]{c,v,t}:
  69,9,"Fir'awna e mofte adinooﾉ兎 mo ﾉ兎n, e ca'e lettiranooﾉ容 wayliteede ﾉ容n, woni yimﾉ兎 Luutu ﾉ兎n, ﾉ兎 ardi e kuuﾉ容 bonﾉ容 immorde e sirku e geddi."
  69,10,"Kala maﾉ橡兎 yeddi Nulaaﾉ熔 mun on, ﾉ兎 fenni mo; Allah nanngiri ﾉ兎 nanngal ﾉ兎ydiingal ko O timminta halkude ﾉ兎."
  69,11,"Ko Menen woni, fewndo ndiyam ﾉ預m hummbunoo, ronndinoo ﾉ兎n wonunooﾉ兎 keeceele mon ka laana dogayka, ka Annabi Nuuhu lesunoo e yamiroore Amen, fii ko waﾉ遼熔ﾉ熔n e mun."
  69,12,"Men waﾉ擁ri kan laana e fillayee makka on, waaju ko dallinoree e halkeede yedduﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n, daﾉ溶da gomﾉ擁mﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n, nowru nanayndu nana ﾉ蓉m."
  69,13,"Si Malaa'ikaajo halfinaaﾉ熔 wuttugol on ka allaandu wuttii wuttaande wootere, ko ndeen woni ﾉ擁ﾉ預ﾉ妬ire nden."
  69,14,"Leydi ndin e pelle ﾉ容n ﾉ殿mtee, ﾉ容 mo ﾉ禿ｱﾃｱe mo ﾉ禿ｱﾃｱannde sattunde, pecce leydi ndi e pelle ﾉ容 sewi."
  69,15,"Nden ﾉ蓉m fow waﾉ預ta, Darngal ngal daroo."
  69,16,"Kammu ngun seekora nden ﾃｱalnde, sabu jippagol Malaa'ika'en, hara hingu lo'i, ﾉ殿awo ngu wonnde sattungu jogondirngu."
  69,17,"Hara Malaa'ika'en no wontiri ka seraaji maggu, njeetato e Malaa'ikaaﾉ兎 ﾉ殿nnitaaﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n ronndoo Arsi Joomi maa kin nden ﾃｱalnde."
  69,18,"Nden ﾃｱalnde, ko onon weeﾉ妬tetee ka Allah, onon ﾉ兎e yimﾉ兎. Hay huunde e fii mon suuﾉ熔taako Mo. Allah ko ﾆｴellitoto fii maﾉ橡兎 on fow."
  69,19,"Si ko jonnitiroyaaﾉ熔 talkuru golle mun ﾉ容n ka ﾃｱaamo mun, on weltoroyay wi'ugol : Jaﾉ兎e ! Janngon talkuru golle am ﾉ容n."
  69,20,"Min mi fellitu ka aduna, wonnde mi immmintinoyte, mi hawra e njoﾉ電i am ndin."
  69,21,"Hara himo e nguurndam welﾉ預m, hakkee neema duumiiﾉ熔 ko o yi'ata."
  69,22,"E nder Aljanna toowuﾉ熔 nokku e darja."
  69,23,"Aljanna mo teﾉ殿teeriiji mun weli heﾉ砥de."
  69,24,"ﾆ‘ teddiniree wi'aneede : ﾃｱaamee yariron ko lorra woo alaa e mu'un, sabu ko ardinirﾉ熔n kon golle moﾆｴﾆｴe e ﾃｱalaaﾉ容 feﾆｴﾆｴunooﾉ容 aduna."
  69,25,"Si tawii non ko jonnitiraaﾉ熔 talkuru golle mun ﾉ容n ka nano mun, on wi'oyay : Ee bone am! Haananiino lam hara mi joniitaaka talkuru golle am ﾉ容n, sabu kuuﾉ容 bone ko woni e mayru kon, waﾉ預ta haa mi lettee."
  69,26,"Hara mi anndaali hay huunde e ko wonata ﾃｱaawoore am."
  69,27,"Hara maayde am nden wonuno timmoode am nde immintiﾅ逆aake e mun fes."
  69,28,"Jawdi am ndin nafiraali lam duﾃｱangol lam lette Allah ﾉ容n."
  69,29,"Cemmbe e jaahu am ko mi wallitoraynoo fow bonntirii lam."
  69,30,"Malaa'ika'en wi'anee : nanngee mo, kombon mo haa e daande."
  69,31,"Refti naadon mo ka Yiite fii no o meeﾉ擁ra nguleendi magge."
  69,32,"Refti naadon mo e nder jolokooje ﾉ容 junndi mun woni cappanﾉ容 jeeﾉ擁ﾉ擁 sogonal."
  69,33,"Tawde pellet, o gomﾉ擁naano Allah Mawﾉ熔 On."
  69,34,"O reerﾉ擁ntaano woﾉ遼兎 goo e ﾃｱammingol miskiino."
